         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"The fourth year of Marcus Aurelius Antoninus Pius Felix Augustus, Phaophi 5. I have received from Pasion on account of Aurelius, the Elder, of the same year 4 drachmas; Hathyr 5, another 4 drachmas; Tybi 9, likewise another 4 drachmas, (drachmas) 4; Pharmouthi . , another 4 drachmas, (drachmas) 4; Epeiph 3, another 4 drachmas, (drachmas)4."</ab>
